        "setup": "Create an app in [Your Apps](https://api.slack.com/apps), add the needed OAuth scopes in **OAuth & Permissions**, then install the app to your workspace or organization to receive a token. Slack's token docs describe bot tokens (`xoxb-`), user tokens (`xoxp-`), and configuration tokens for manifest APIs.",
